rusty-wire (2.20.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Configurable hybrid section split (--hybrid-split s1,s2,s3): validated ratio propagated through CLI, TUI, session persistence, and per-band display.
  * TUI: new Hybrid Split config field with four presets cycled with left/right arrows.
  * Session files gain hybrid_section_split with backward-compatible serde default.

